          "reviewBody": "It is a very good educational co-ed school with good atmosphere and it is a proud for us to study in this school and the teacher teach us in such a manner so that we understand or understood every thing\nWe never have doubt in any subject\nAnd also we where score well in Exams.\nOur honourable Principal mam, teachers, School staff and other office staff are  well behave and help school with students to go up in future. There are some rules of school which we all students obey. In each section there are 30 to 34 students and there where 3 section named as Section A, Section B Section C. In this school all students are come from a good family and background. So that no students harms or broke any school property .This school have three branch first is Garcha branch school, belighata school and Sarat bose School. These are the area name. I feel proud to say that I am a hartley students. Probably there are 700 students.\nThis is a school from Class 1 to Class 12 .\nEvery year school paints there wall. Board exams and inter exams are always take place in this school.",
